# Rycode — Netlify redirects
# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# The GRC case-study page links out to https://grc.rycode.dev/,
# which is the GRC site's own custom domain on its own Netlify
# project. We do NOT proxy /grc/* from here — Netlify's Pro
# password-protection renders a login form that only works when
# served from the origin's own domain, not through a rewrite.
#
# This file is intentionally left without rules. Add redirects
# below as the site grows.
